            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-10-15T17:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-07-28T18:00:00-05:00" n="282" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d282">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.U.36.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 27</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00">undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>At the end, add a new paragraph 3, as follows: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>3. Neither the Allied and Associated Powers whose territory was occupied
                            by Hungary and to whom, under the present Treaty, Hungary is required to
                            pay reparations, nor their nationals will refund any amounts due to
                            Hungary or to Hungarian nationals.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
